de.iabg.mode
Class JModeCorrelationPanel

java.lang.Object
  java.awt.Component
      java.awt.Container
          javax.swing.JComponent
              javax.swing.JPanel
                  de.iabg.mode.JModeCorrelationPanel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Renderable, Loggable, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
public class JModeCorrelationPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements Loggable, Renderable

An implementation for for correlating two mode shape matrices. This component can import geometric data, mode shape data, and mass matrix data. With this data, this component can compute modal correlations and modal connections, and export those correlations and connections for later use. Refer to ModeCorrelationModel class API for more details.

Version:
September 12, 2008
Author:
Adam C. Dick, BSE
